{"lemma":"مَغْفُورُ","slug":"مَغْفُورُ","root":"غ.ف.ر","root_slug":"غ-ف-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ف-ر","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32124"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%BA%D9%92%D9%81%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"passive participle of غَفَرَ (ḡafara)","tags":["form-of","participle","passive"],"examples":[{"text":"حَجًّا مَبْرُورًا وَسَعِْيًا مَشْكُورًا وَذَنْبًا مَغْفُورًا","english":"May Allah accept your Hajj, reward you for your efforts and grant you forgiveness."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"passive participle of غَفَرَ (ḡafara); forgiven, pardoned"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"passive participle of غَفَرَ (ḡafara); deceased (wishing him forgiveness for his sins) (always used with the preposition لِ (li))"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the passive participle of the verb غَفَرَ (ḡafara, “to forgive”)."},"ipa":["/maɣ.fuːr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32124","headword_ar":"مُغْفُورٌ","root":"gfr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, T, S, K, &c.) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migofarN","text_ar":"مِغْفَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, T, S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugofarN","text_ar":"مُغْفَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migofaArN","text_ar":"مِغْفَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migofyrN","text_ar":"مِغْفيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugovuwrN","text_ar":"مُغْثُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, S, K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of manna;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a produce of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species of tree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shrub, called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimov","text_ar":"رِمْث"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and sometimes of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu$ar","text_ar":"عُشَر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurofuT","text_ar":"عُرْفُط"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAm","text_ar":"ثُمَام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salam","text_ar":"سَلَم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaloH","text_ar":"طَلْح"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gum of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rmv","text_ar":"رمث"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ErfT","text_ar":"عرفط"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gum that is found upon the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rmv","text_ar":"رمث"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is sweet, and is eaten;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that flows,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exudes, from the ends of the twigs of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rmv","text_ar":"رمث"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dibos","text_ar":"دِبْس"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its colour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, in explanation of the pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magaAfiyru","text_ar":"مَغَافِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":";)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gum that flows,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exudes, from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ErfT","text_ar":"عرفط"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not of pleasant odour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gum resembling"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the kind of sweetmeat called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naATif","text_ar":"نَاطِف"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exuded by the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ErfT","text_ar":"عرفط"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is put into a piece of cloth, then sprinkled with water, and drunk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to Lth, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migofaArN","text_ar":"مِغْفَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gum of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ij~aASap","text_ar":"اـِجَّاصَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": and some say that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migofarN","text_ar":"مِغْفَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gum of a round shape;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuEoruwrN","text_ar":"صُعْرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to that which is in shape like a finger; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awobN","text_ar":"ذَوْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to that which flows upon the ground: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migofarN","text_ar":"مِغْفَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a twig of a gum-tree, from which"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(with which), in the TA, I read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu","text_ar":"مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is wiped a white fluid, whereof is made a sweet beverage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugofuwrN","text_ar":"مُغْفُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migofaArN","text_ar":"مِغْفَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migofiyrN","text_ar":"مِغْفِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magaAfiyru","text_ar":"مَغَافِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, K,) and [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migofarN","text_ar":"مِغْفَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugofurN","text_ar":"مُغْفُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magaAfiru","text_ar":"مَغَافِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) it is also said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magaAfiyru","text_ar":"مَغَافِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a kind of sweet honey, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rub~","text_ar":"رُبّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"except that it is white."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [Hence the saying,]"},{"kind":"quote","text":"↓ \n      h`*aA AljanaY laA A^aono yukad~a Almugofuru"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is gathering, not the scraping off"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mgfr","text_ar":"مغفر"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: a prov. alluding to the preference of a thing; said to him who obtains much good. (K.) [See also Freytag's Arab. Prov., ii. 874.]"}],"source_refs":["Ks","T","S","K","TA"]}]}}